title: DAZ3D - Fantasy Features for Genesis 3 Female(s)
description:
USER & MERCHANT RESOURCE

Turn any of your Genesis 3 Female figures into a pure Fantasy character with custom ears, noses, mouth or teeth and even more !

If you're a vendor, you can use those morphs commercially and include them in your future character sets with no additional cost.

This set includes 50 different custom morphs that can be combined together or with existing morphs (see promo images for complete list and their thumbnails). you can even reverse them (negative values on Dial) for a unique and surprising effect!

All the promos have been made using Daz Original characters and their original textures, and simply applying the Fantasy Features morphs and changing the shaders.

What's Included and Features

Fantasy Features Reset Morphs Preset (.DUF)
Fantasy Features Morph List Script (.DSA)
